        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "Labor Department of Chhattisgarh State started this scheme &quot;Mukhyamantri Asangathit Karmakaar Saayakal Sahaayata Yojana&quot; for unorganized worker on 28 April 2012. Under this scheme, One cycle will be provided free of cost to each women beneficiary. The main objective of the scheme to empower the unorganized female worker through provide them free cycle. \n",
        "benefits_md": "> A free of cost cycle will be provided. \n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "> Applicant must not have received a sewing machine under the Sewing Machine Assistance Scheme implemented by the Board or any other government scheme.\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "Chhattisgarh State Government started a scheme \"Mukhyamantri Asangathit Karmakaar Saayakal Sahaayata Yojana\" for unorganized worker on 28 April 2012.",
